{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["/documentation/swift/asyncthrowingcompactmapsequence/flatmap(_:)-1xasg"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/AsyncThrowingCompactMapSequence/flatMap(_:)-1xasg"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Creates an asynchronous sequence that concatenates the results of calling","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the given error-throwing transformation with each element of this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sequence."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@preconcurrency"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"flatMap"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"genericParameter","text":"SegmentOfResult"},{"text":">(","kind":"text"},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"transform","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@Sendable","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"@escaping","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/AsyncSequence/Element","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sci7ElementQa","text":"Element","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"async","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sci12_ConcurrencyE7flatMapyAA017AsyncThrowingFlatC8SequenceVyxqd__Gqd__7ElementQzYaKcSciRd__lF15SegmentOfResultL_qd__mfp","text":"SegmentOfResult","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/AsyncThrowingFlatMapSequence","preciseIdentifier":"s:12_Concurrency28AsyncThrowingFlatMapSequenceV","text":"AsyncThrowingFlatMapSequence","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"Self","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sci12_ConcurrencyE7flatMapyAA017AsyncThrowingFlatC8SequenceVyxqd__Gqd__7ElementQzYaKcSciRd__lF15SegmentOfResultL_qd__mfp","text":"SegmentOfResult","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"where","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SegmentOfResult","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/AsyncSequence","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sci","text":"AsyncSequence","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"transform","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An error-throwing mapping closure. "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transform"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"accepts an element of this sequence as its parameter and returns an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AsyncSequence"},{"type":"text","text":". If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transform"},{"type":"text","text":" throws an error, the sequence ends."}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A single, flattened asynchronous sequence that contains all"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"elements in all the asynchronous sequences produced by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transform"},{"type":"text","text":". The"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sequence ends either when the last sequence created from the last"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"element from base sequence ends, or when "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transform"},{"type":"text","text":" throws an error."}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this method to receive a single-level asynchronous sequence when your"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"transformation produces an asynchronous sequence for each element."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In this example, an asynchronous sequence called "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Counter"},{"type":"text","text":" produces "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Int"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"values from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"1"},{"type":"text","text":" to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"5"},{"type":"text","text":". The transforming closure takes the received "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Int"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and returns a new "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Counter"},{"type":"text","text":" that counts that high. For example, when the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"transform receives "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"3"},{"type":"text","text":" from the base sequence, it creates a new "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Counter"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that produces the values "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"1"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"2"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"3"},{"type":"text","text":". The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"flatMap(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" method"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"“flattens” the resulting sequence-of-sequences into a single"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AsyncSequence"},{"type":"text","text":". However, when the closure receives "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"4"},{"type":"text","text":", it throws an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"error, terminating the sequence."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["do {","    let stream = Counter(howHigh: 5)","        .flatMap { (value) -> Counter in","            if value == 4 {","                throw MyError()","            }","            return Counter(howHigh: value)","        }","    for try await number in stream {","        print(number, terminator: \" \")","    }","} catch {","    print(error)","}","// Prints \"1 1 2 1 2 3 MyError() \""]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift","doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/AsyncThrowingCompactMapSequence"]]},"metadata":{"title":"flatMap(_:)","externalID":"s:Sci12_ConcurrencyE7flatMapyAA017AsyncThrowingFlatC8SequenceVyxqd__Gqd__7ElementQzYaKcSciRd__lF::SYNTHESIZED::s:12_Concurrency31AsyncThrowingCompactMapSequenceV","modules":[{"name":"Swift","relatedModules":[]}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"flatMap"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"genericParameter","text":"SegmentOfResult"},{"kind":"text","text":">("},{"kind":"attribute","text":"@Sendable"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Element","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sci7ElementQa"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"async"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"},{"kind":"text","text":" -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SegmentOfResult","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sci12_ConcurrencyE7flatMapyAA017AsyncThrowingFlatC8SequenceVyxqd__Gqd__7ElementQzYaKcSciRd__lF15SegmentOfResultL_qd__mfp"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:12_Concurrency28AsyncThrowingFlatMapSequenceV","text":"AsyncThrowingFlatMapSequence"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Self"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sci12_ConcurrencyE7flatMapyAA017AsyncThrowingFlatC8SequenceVyxqd__Gqd__7ElementQzYaKcSciRd__lF15SegmentOfResultL_qd__mfp","text":"SegmentOfResult"},{"kind":"text","text":">"}],"extendedModule":"_Concurrency","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Ins